{
  "stem": "8784.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He fought in six wars in Israel, and he is now deceased too; Olek Allerhand, who did survive with me, is in Israel now.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were a bunch of others.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a fellow by the name of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were all young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Bejski-- this is the brother of Justice Bejski of Israel-- was a close friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was the-- this friend of mine, by the name of Bejski-- and I don't remember his first name at the moment-- but-- but he was the valet for Oskar Schindler.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a close circle of people that we kept in touch with.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- in fact, after Schindler declared that we are free people, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] people began to think on what we do next.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I walked around with this memoir, getting people to sign their names so I would remember them a bit longer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We began to scheme on what we do from now on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a group of people-- one of them, the leader was one of the people that worked with me in the woodworking shop-- began to put together a group of people that would take off after a few days and go towards Krakow, Poland.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the intention of that group was to do it quickly opposed to some people who remained in the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Number one, some of them were not strong enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Number two, some of them hesitated to go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This group was planning to go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In retrospect, looking at it and thinking about this plan, it was a poorly hatched plan, again, because we had no idea where we were.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
